description:
If you or a loved one was injured in an accident caused by the negligence of another person, the New Jersey personal injury lawyers at Levinson Axelrod, P.A., can help. Contact our Jamesburg office to discuss your matter during a no-cost consultation. After listening to the facts of your situation, we will provide a free case evaluation.

We offer 100 percent FREE case evaluations to help determine if you have sufficient grounds to file a lawsuit, and we only get paid if we win your case.

A serious accident can result in devastating injuries such as traumatic brain injuries (TBI), paralysis or amputation. These catastrophic injuries can lead to a lifetime of medical care, diminished earning potential and costly lifestyle changes. Let Levinson Axelrod, P.A., fight for your maximum compensation. We will attempt to negotiate a settlement with the negligent party's insurance carrier that accounts for your lost wages, medical bills, property damage, and pain and suffering. If a settlement cannot be reached, we are confident in our ability to represent you in court.

Celebrating 80 years of practice.

Whether your injury was the result of a motor vehicle accident, dangerous product or premises liability, an experienced law firm can help. Schedule a consultation with a knowledgeable attorney today to learn more about your legal options for monetary recovery.

Contact our law firm to schedule a free consultation and receive an honest case evaluation. We maintain seven area offices for the convenience of our clients.
